name: CI ONE Global Equity ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of the CI ONE Global Equity ETF (the Fund) is to seek longterm growth. The fund investing in a portfolio of equity securities of global issuers, through direct purchases of publicly traded companies andor exchange traded funds that represent an equity asset class. The Fund seeks geographic diversification in Canada, U.S., developed markets in Europe and Asia, and developing markets. The Fund is diversified by market capitalization from large cap companies to micro-cap companies around the world. The Fund tends to include exposure to publicly traded real estate investment trusts (REITs).
